    "title": "Spicy Beetroot, Leek & Walnut Salad",
    "description": "A gutsy salad with Georgian inspiration featuring roasted beetroot and leeks, combined with walnuts, herbs, and a flavorful dressing.",
    "servings": 4,
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "totalTime": "2h",
